OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAny morning showery outbreaks
OL,6,Ffading, then generally dry with bright
OL,7,For sunny spells developing for the
OL,8,Fafternoon. Cloud increasing later in
OL,9,Fthe evening with a risk of some
OL,10,Fshowery rain. Mostly light or gentle
OL,11,Fwinds.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FAny showery outbreaks of rain
OL,14,Fat first, will gradually weaken
OL,15,Fovernight to leave a rather cloudy,
OL,16,Fbut mainly dry start to Tuesday. Winds
OL,17,Fremaining generally light.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
