OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FGenerally dry with variable
OL,6,Fcloud but warm, sunny spells
OL,7,Fdeveloping. Thicker cloud with some
OL,8,Frain gradually extending east through
OL,9,Fthe evening. Turning breezier later.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,12,FCloudier on Wednesday with some patchy
OL,13,Frain. Thursday and Friday, mostly dry
OL,14,Fwith bright or sunny spells. Turning
OL,15,Fvery warm, perhaps locally hot, and
OL,16,Ffeeling increasingly humid. Thundery
OL,17,Fshowers possible.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
